Insider Activity


Individual




David C. Dauch



Mr. David C. Dauch is Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at American Axle & Manufacturing Holdings, Inc., Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer at American Axle & Manufacturing, Inc., and a Director at Horizon Global Corp. He is on the Board of Directors at Amerisure Mutual Insurance Co., Boys & Girls Club of Southeastern Michigan, Business Leaders for Michigan, Detroit Regional Chamber of Commerce, Great Lakes Council, Boy Scouts of America, Original Equipment Suppliers Association, Horizon Global Corp., Amerisure Mutual Holdings, Inc., and Detroit Economic Club.
Mr. Dauch was previously employed as a Sales Associate by Collins & Aikman Products LLC. He also served on the board at Collins & Aikman Corp.
He received his undergraduate degree from Miami University (Ohio) and an MBA from Michigan State University.



