Background

		Mr. David C. Dauch has been Chairman and Chief Executive Officer at Metaldyne Performance Group Inc. since April 6, 2017. Mr. Dauch has been the Chairman of the Board and Chief Executive Officer of American Axle & Manufacturing Holdings, Inc. since September 1, 2012. Mr. Dauch has been Chief Executive Officer at American Axle & Manufacturing, Inc. since September 2012 and its Chairman since August 2013. He served as President at American Axle & Manufacturing Holdings, ... Inc. from June 1, 2008 to August 2015 He served as the Chief Operating Officer of American Axle & Manufacturing, Inc. from November 2007 to September 2012 and its President from June 1, 2008 to August 6, 2015. He served as the Chief Operating Officer of American Axle & Manufacturing Holdings, Inc. from 2008 to September 1, 2012. He served as an Executive Vice President of American Axle & Manufacturing, Inc. and American Axle & Manufacturing Holdings, Inc. from December 2007 to June 2008. He served as Executive Vice President of Commercial and Strategic Development at American Axle & Manufacturing Holdings, Inc. and American Axle & Manufacturing, Inc. from January 2005 to November 2007. He served as Senior Vice President of Commercial at American Axle & Manufacturing Holdings, Inc. from June 2004 to January 2005 and served as its Vice President of Manufacturing of Driveline Division from January 2001 to September 2003. He served as Senior Vice President of Sales and Marketing of Driveline Division at American Axle & Manufacturing Holdings, Inc. from September 2003 to May 2004. He served as Vice President of Sales & Marketing from 1998 to January 2001. He joined American Axle & Manufacturing Holdings, Inc. in 1995 as Manager of Sales Administration. Mr. Dauch held various positions at Collins & Aikman Products Company, including Sales Manager. From 1987 to 1995, he served at Products where he held positions of product manager, account executive and Director of Ford Sales and Marketing at the Automotive Carpet and Fabric Groups. He has been the Chairman of American Axle & Manufacturing Holdings, Inc. since August 16, 2013 and has been its Director since April 1, 2009. He has been a Director of American Axle & Manufacturing, Inc., since April 2009. He serves as Director of Amerisure Mutual Insurance Company, Inc. He serves as a Director of Business Leaders for Michigan. He has been a Director at Horizon Global Corporation since June 29, 2015. He served as a Director of Collins & Aikman Corp. (now Collins & Aikman LLC) since 2002. He served as a Director of Sales of GM Full-Size Truck Programs from May 1996 to 1998. Mr. Dauch holds Bachelor of Science Degrees in Production/Operations and Purchasing Management from Miami University (Ohio) and Master of Business Administration from Michigan State University.Read Full Background




