Amerisure Elects David C. Dauch to Board of Directors


12/23/2014
Farmington Hills, Mich., Dec. 23, 2014—The Amerisure Companies announce the election of David C. Dauch to the Board of Directors of Amerisure Mutual Holdings, Inc. and the Amerisure Companies.

 


Dauch is Chairman, President and Chief Executive Officer of American Axle & Manufacturing, Inc. (AAM), a position he has held since August 2013. He joined AAM in July 1995 and has served in positions of increasing responsibility, including most recently, President and Chief Executive Officer. Prior to joining AAM, Dauch held positions at Collins & Aikman Products Company, where he received the President's Award for leadership and innovation.

"I am pleased to welcome David to our Board of Directors," said Gregory J. Crabb, President and Chief Executive Officer of Amerisure Insurance Companies. "Amerisure’s Board of Directors is one of the cornerstones upon which we have built and carried out our strong corporate governance oversight."

In addition to his board position at Amerisure, Dauch serves on the Boards of Directors of AAM, Business Leaders for Michigan, the Detroit Regional Chamber, the Great Lakes Council Boy Scouts of America and the Boys & Girls Clubs of Southeastern Michigan. Dauch also serves on the Miami University Business Advisory Council.

Dauch joins current Amerisure Directors Karen Batchelor, Robert K. Burgess, Charles B. Coe, Gregory J. Crabb, Dennis R. Herrick, Phillip E. Love, Jr., James B. Nicholson, James M. Nicholson and Bettina M. Whyte.
 
About Amerisure Insurance
Amerisure Mutual Insurance Company, a stock insurer, is a property and casualty insurance company with experience insuring American businesses since 1912. Amerisure and its affiliates target mid-sized commercial enterprises in manufacturing, construction and healthcare through strategically located Core Service Centers across the United States. For more information, visit www.amerisure.com.


Press Contact
If you would like more information on Amerisure, please contact:

Amy Neale
Marketing Communications Specialist
(248) 426-7914
aneale@amerisure.com
 


